aph, today, what Stieglitz himself made it over the years—a photo-text work.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aCollections, Catalogs, Exhibitions. 4aGeneral. 4aPhotography. 7aPhotography / Collections, Catalogs, Exhibitions / General.2bisacsh1 aFrancisco, Jason, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrancisco, Jason, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLee, Anthony W., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLee, Anthony W., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMcCauley, Elizabeth Anne, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMccauley, Elizabeth Anne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z97831106904220 cprintz978052026623040uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052035247640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520352476423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520352476/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles